FBIS3-15579 "drsov045_m_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-045 Document Type:Daily Report 8 Mar 1994 Tajikistan Russian Border Guards Under Fire From Afghan Territory LD0703122394 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1000 GMT 7 Mar 94 LD0703122394 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Russia's 11th border unit of the Pyandzh detachment in Tajikistan came under machinegun fire from Afghan territory on the evening of 6 March, INTERFAX learned at the headquarters of the Russian border troops in Tajikistan. There were no casualties among the border troops, and they did not return fire.
